How to run tests of RubyStation
===============================

Spec
----

1. install rspec
    $ gem intall rspec

2. run test

    $ rake spec

Features
--------

1. install cucumber:
    $ gem install cucumber

2. install jruby (http://jruby.org/) and celerity

JRuby must be executable by 'jruby'.

    $ jgem install celerity

3. install culerity:
    $ gem install culerity

4. run test
    $ rake cucumber




